research_municipality_step.notes: Joshua, TX operates under a Council-City Manager form of government, which aligns with the 'mayor_council' type. All council members are elected at large. There was a discrepancy for Council Member Place 1, with one source listing Johnny Waldrip and multiple other sources, including the city's own meeting directory, listing Dustin Dees. Dustin Dees was chosen based on the majority and more recent information from the city's official sources.
